cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.LG 

This paper deals with analyzing user behavior on online platforms, specifically in relation to badges. This falls under the category of social media analysis, which is covered by cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.CY (Computers and Society). The paper also uses statistical and machine learning techniques to analyze user behavior, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper discusses the impact of badges on user behavior, which could be relevant to cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
